[gd_resource type="Theme" format=3 uid="uid://cjkitthemedef01"]

; Default theme for the Journey Engine UI kit. Muted indigo on near-black — readable
; long-form narrative, distinct from Godot's own blue. To restyle YOUR game,
; DUPLICATE this into res://<your_game>/ui/ and assign it to JourneyView.theme.
; Do NOT edit this addon copy — a kit update would overwrite it.

